import org.apache.spark.{SparkConf, SparkContext}
import org.apache.spark.sql.SparkSession
import org.apache.spark.sql._
import org.apache.spark.sql.types.{StructType, StructField, StringType}

val schemaStringRep = "year state state_po state_flips state_cen state_ic office district stage runoff special  party writein mode candidates_votes total_votes unofficial version fusion_ticket"
val repFile = sc.textFile("/data/Project2Data_USRepresentatives.csv")


val schemaRep = StructType(schemaStringRep.split(" ").map(fieldName => StructField(fieldName, StringType,true)))
val rowRDDRep= repFile.map(_.split(",")).map(p=> Row(p(0),p(1), p(2), p(3), p(4),p(5),p(6),p(7),p(8),p(9),p(10),p(11),p(12),p(13),p(14),p(15),p(16),p(17),p(18),p(19)))
var candidatesRepDF = sqlContext.createDataFrame(rowRDDRep, schemaRep)

val header = candidatesRepDF.first
val candidatesRepDF2 = candidatesRepDF.filter(line => line != header)

candidatesRepDF2.createOrReplaceTempView("candidatesRep")
